<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Nördlingen</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Auskunft wegen Anerkennung des Pfalzgrafen Ludwig III. als Reichsvikar.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_144" id="71v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_144_r2l18"><expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_144_r2l19"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> Es ſind etc ſchreibt / . vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an vns begert daʒ vvir Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l20">dafür <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> / Nu iſt vns geſagt <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vvie das auch in <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l21">maʒʒ an ew braht ſeÿ / vnd daʒ Jr Jm das cʒügeſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſüllet / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_144_r2l22"><expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc vvie Jr ſein gnaden etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>Sup<ex>ra</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_144" id="71v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, es sind etc. schreibt und
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> an uns begert, daz wir in dafür
                                <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sülle<ex>n</ex></expan>. Nu ist uns gesagt
                            <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie das auch in
                            <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> mazz an ew braht sey und daz ir im das
                        czügesagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> süllet.
                            <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc., wie ir sein gnaden etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
